						               													<description>Big Time Hoops is a fast-playing, card-based simulation of professional basketball for two players. To recreate the flow of the game and remove &amp;quot;housekeeping&amp;quot; altogether, the game eschews individual cards for basketball players and focuses exclusively on the major action elements of the sport.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In general, you'll hold a hand of three cards, most of which will be offensive in nature. You'll play one of them, choosing to pass the ball or drive to the basket; each card will result in a shot attempt with a varying degree of success. Then you'll roll a die. If the shot fails, the card states which side gets the rebound. (Yes, three-point shots are in the game.)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Your opponent can play a defensive card, and when used wisely he'll steal a pass, block a shot or foul your shooter.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Simulating realistic scoring requires a delicate balance in a sport where each team averages 100 points per game. Rest assured that you'll find it here, as the number of two-pointers, three-pointers and foul shots will be very close to their actual real-life averages each and every game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Playable in an hour, Big Time Hoops will provide all the fun and excitement of real pro basketball -- without the high ticket prices!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
